{"tid":1827263,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"毛主席係我地既偶像，每個連登仔都要學習！","createTime":"2020-01-16T23:15:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-17T02:13:05.000Z","uid":30067,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"aaa225ea6e9a3be36956a323557188de13c247e8","tid":1827263,"uid":30067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T23:15:49.000Z","msg":"革命不是請客吃飯，不是做文章，不是繪畫綉花，不能那樣雅致，那樣從容不迫，文質彬彬，那樣溫良恭儉讓。革命是暴動，是一個階級推翻另一個階級的暴烈的行動。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xBzP3mv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxBzP3mv.jpg&h=a34d4e25&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"01e55bdd8ef4c39bea237d08b219870aa7682c33","tid":1827263,"uid":30067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T23:15:59.000Z","msg":"凡是敵人反對的，我們就要擁護；凡是敵人擁護的，我們就要反對。"},{"pid":"0316c8641e1aa831fd61d576be030e07c493eb0a","tid":1827263,"uid":30067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T23:16:12.000Z","msg":"真正強大的力量不是屬於反動派，而是屬於人民。"},{"pid":"6e0035a554c56b589f99c9c613b38c16c7255ab2","tid":1827263,"uid":30067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T23:17:19.000Z","msg":"如若不被敵人反對，那就不好了，那一定是同敵人同流合污了。如若被敵人反對，那就好了，那就證明我們同敵人劃清界線了。"},{"pid":"fc2ba0d515247497bb4a827957ed3d74fe9a1071","tid":1827263,"uid":30067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T23:18:07.000Z","msg":"人民萬歲！革命無罪，造反有理！ 哪裏有壓迫哪裏就有反抗! 不要被糖衣炮彈打倒。"},{"pid":"a9ff3fbcdccdeb34c1a73b1ff72a41b9fd20a3ef","tid":1827263,"uid":30067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T23:18:31.000Z","msg":"究竟是一個黨好，還是幾個黨好？現在看來，恐怕是幾個黨好。"},{"pid":"430cf1e781ad945f97dd8dadb322a9d202fa21ac","tid":1827263,"uid":30067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T23:18:49.000Z","msg":"情況是在不斷地變化，要使自己的思想適應新的情況，就得學習。"},{"pid":"f93e785544d8c9f7d8325a5e69466f368afd6b2c","tid":1827263,"uid":30067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T23:20:42.000Z","msg":"首先，<del>蘇聯</del>、美國是第一世界；其次，中間派，日本、歐洲、加拿大，是第二世界；最后，亞洲(除了日本)、非洲和拉丁美洲是第三世界。"},{"pid":"4c104bf0b01ec706e01980e925bfc0181ed1690a","tid":1827263,"uid":30067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T23:22:02.000Z","msg":"誰是我們的敵人，誰是我們的朋友，這是革命的首要問題。"},{"pid":"f91b96013778e3a1add2efc04707b15339d7010c","tid":1827263,"uid":30067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T23:22:13.000Z","msg":"自推十回完畢"},{"pid":"e664a3b2638d2825387a63a3d8c11a83e83b415a","tid":1827263,"uid":30067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T02:13:05.000Z","msg":"推"}]}